          <a href="/government/organisations/department-of-health-and-social-care">Department of Health and Social Care homepage</a>
</p>        <h1 class="main">Statistics at DHSC</h1>
        <p class="description">
          Official statistics published by the Department of Health.
        </p>
        <div class="body">
          <div class="govspeak">
<h2 id="statistical-series">Statistical series</h2>

<p>The Department of Health (<abbr title="Department of Health">DH</abbr>) publishes annual statistics on abortion for England and Wales. <abbr title="Department of Health">DH</abbr> also publishes one off and time limited statistics as needed. These statistics are used to inform debate, decision making and research both within government and by the wider community.</p>

<p><a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/collections/abortion-statistics-for-england-and-wales">Abortion statistics</a></p>

